cu.explanation_en: Modified amf_ip_address.ipv4 to '192.168.70.256', which is an invalid IP address (octet 256 > 255), causing unreachable AMF and routing misconfiguration in CU.

du.explanation_en: Modified ul_carrierBandwidth to 500, which is out of the valid range for NR band 78 (typically 5-100 MHz), causing out_of_range error in DU configuration.
